    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait but if i take the insulin with no carbs in my system wont that definitely make me go low? i was reading online that if you dont eat much you can skip or reduce it to avoid hypoglycemia. wouldnt it be safer to just skip it this once if i'm worried about crashing?",
