      "content": "I can see why you'd think that, but trust me, skipping the basal dose won't help, and it's actually a recipe for disaster. Your body's insulin sensitivity is affected by the timing of the dose, not the timing of your meals. Skipping it will just delay the crash, and when it does happen, it'll be worse. I'm telling you, it's better to take the basal dose as scheduled, even if you're not hungry.",
