      "content": "i just don't feel comfortable with the idea of it being a \"recipe for disaster\" if i only missed one dose. my doctor isn't around right now and i really dont want to wake up at 3am with a massive sugar spike because i didnt take it. can you just tell me straight, if i take a half dose instead of skipping it entirely, is that a safe middle ground to avoid the low? please just give me a straight answer so i can sleep.",
